      <title>工党称下一届英国政府面临战后最糟糕的继承</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/labour-says-next-uk-government-faces-worst-inheritance-since-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[影子财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯表示，英国反对党工党如果赢得下次选举，将面临二战以来最糟糕的经济遗产，因为执政的保守党已经花费了太多钱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/labour-says-next-uk-government-faces-worst-inheritance-since-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 17:35:09 GMT</pubDate>
