      <title>埃及在价值 350 亿美元的土地交易后获得阿联酋的第一笔付款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/egypt-has-received-part-of-35-billion-in-uae-funds-sisi-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃及已收到阿拉伯联合酋长国承诺的 350 亿美元资金的第一笔转账，这是一笔巨额融资，将进一步推动货币贬值，并有望释放更多国际援助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/egypt-has-received-part-of-35-billion-in-uae-funds-sisi-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 11:33:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合国称四分之一的加沙人距离饥荒“仅一步之遥”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-27/one-in-four-gazans-are-now-one-step-away-from-famine-un-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国警告说，加沙地带四分之一的人距离经历饥荒“仅一步之遥”，并表示，随着人道主义机构报告向饱受战争蹂躏的地区运送援助遇到困难，情况将进一步恶化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-27/one-in-four-gazans-are-now-one-step-away-from-famine-un-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 21:54:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
